00:02:29.350 --> 00:02:33.710
the ratio of area to side,

00:02:33.710 --> 00:02:35.940
to side length.

00:02:35.940 --> 00:02:38.620
So here the ratio's one over one,

00:02:38.620 --> 00:02:41.281
one over one, which equals one.

00:02:41.281 --> 00:02:42.850
Now that seems reasonable.

00:02:42.850 --> 00:02:44.620
For this next one the ratio of

00:02:44.620 --> 00:02:47.820
area over side length is four over two,

00:02:47.820 --> 00:02:51.220
