00:03:06.680 --> 00:03:08.720
so that tells us that these two, that

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:11.790
the side length and the area are not proportional.

00:03:11.790 --> 00:03:14.500
Not, not proportional.

00:03:15.550 --> 00:03:17.650
