00:03:22.290 --> 00:03:23.750
depending on the side length and that's because

00:03:23.750 --> 00:03:26.080
we're squaring things, it's literally,

00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:28.420
you're literally taking x squared,

00:03:28.420 --> 00:03:30.020
if, you know, you have x here,

00:03:30.020 --> 00:03:31.510
this is going to be x squared

00:03:31.510 --> 00:03:35.190
and the ratio is going to be x squared over x,

00:03:35.190 --> 00:03:36.890
which of course is always just going to be

00:03:36.890 --> 00:03:38.990
equal, this is x times x divided by x,

00:03:38.990 --> 00:03:40.590
that's always going to be equal to x,

00:03:40.590 --> 00:03:41.590
